Introduction

Amy Jannet Harvey is a Australian-Japanese rapper, singer, dancer and model under XGALX. She is best known as the main rapper and sub vocalist of the Japanese global girl group XG.

Born in Tokyo, Japan, Harvey was active as a model since she was in junior high school but she wanted to try something new. Which turned into a strong desire to do something that nobody has ever done before and the thing that matched the best was XGALX audition so she wanted to be a part of it which led her to debut in XG.

On February 4, 2022, Harvey was revealed the seventh member of XG. The group officially debuted on Mar 18, 2022, with their debut digital single "Tippy Toes".
